  <li>VPN = <strong>7</strong></li>
  <li>Entry 7 is invalid (V = 0) -&gt; <strong>page fault</strong>
    <ul>
      <li>Virtual page must be paged into physical memory from disk (page fault)</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
